Description:
Send any text (or voice) and the bot returns a translation.
• Auto-detects the source language; remembers your chosen source → target pair after you press “Choose languages”.
• You can override on the fly: write “translate to German …” or “переведи на русский …”.
• Supports 50 + languages, runs on local models—no external data storage.

About:
Universal translator bot: auto-detects source language & instantly translates to your chosen target.
